sequenceDiagram
  participant Worker
  participant Proposal
  participant Manifest
  participant Backup
  participant Vault
  participant Verify

  Worker->>Proposal: emit proposal bundle only
  Proposal->>Manifest: wait for explicit approval
  Manifest->>Backup: create scoped backup plan
  Backup->>Vault: apply approved targets only
  Vault->>Verify: fresh observe and compare
  Verify-->>Worker: report PASS/FAIL evidence
